ia-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 13, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zpb1714306631479.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zpb1714306631479.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zpb1714306631479.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mam1665702538335\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Retrieves field syntax properties that were set in the browser (using the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setSyntaxProperty</span> or <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setSyntaxProperties</span> functions).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mam1665702538335__topic_d126665e1_d126666e1_d126667e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mam1665702538335__p_d126668e1_d126669e1_d126670e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldObject</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code><span class=\"keyword apiname\">getSyntaxProperties</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">()</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mam1665702538335__section_w1113ab1b5b3_w1114ab1b5_w1115ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d143096e76\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mam1665702538335__section_w1116ab1b5b5_w1117ab1b5_w1118ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d143096e85\">Return value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mam1665702538335__parml_hb1_4b5_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">A a JavaScript object with each attribute representing a syntax field property. For\n            example, in JavaScript Object Notation (JSON), such an object is represented\n            as:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zpb1714306631479_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mam1665702538335__codeblock_hg4_nb5_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{\n \"DIG\" : true,\n \"LEN\" : { \"min\" : 3, \"max\" : 5 }\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mam1665702538335__section_w1119ab1b5b7_w1120ab1b5_w1121ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d143096e105\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"shk1665703139073.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" title=\"Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a></code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mam1665702538335__section_w1122ab1b5b9_w1123ab1b5_w1124ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d143096e126\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mam1665702538335__p_d126692e1_d126693e1_d126694e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getSyntaxProperties</span> function\n        only returns properties that were set in the browser using JavaScript, not those that were\n        set in the server before being sent to the browser. The get these properties, use\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getDeclarativeSyntax</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Syntax Properties Supported by the JavaScript API</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">Property</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">JavaScript Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">Values</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Description/Remarks</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NED</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">Unsupported. Use property\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">html:readOnly</code> instead</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">—</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">No edit allowed in this field. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DIM</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">Unsupported. Use property\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">html:disabled</code> instead</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">—</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Dim field. No edit and no prompt.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">REX</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">Uniface entry format as regex string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Regex string for data entry. For example,\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"/[a-z]*/i\"</code> (zero or more [a-zA-Z]). For more information, see\n                  <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jjg1714304600909.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" title=\"Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax Codes</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ENT</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">Uniface entry format as syntax string</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Syntax for data entry. For example,\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"&amp;*\"</code> (zero or more [a-zA-Z]). For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jjg1714304600909.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" title=\"Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax Codes</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LEN</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">object</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">{ min:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">max:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">}</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Length of field or subfield.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ASC</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">ASCII, in Unicode range 00-7F </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">BRM</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Check that brackets match. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DIG</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Digits only (0-9) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DLS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Delete leading spaces. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DLZ</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Delete leading zeros. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LOW</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">All lowercase </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">MAN</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Mandatory field (minimum length of one). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NUM</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Numbers only (0-9, . + -) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">RCS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">Replace contiguous spaces with one space. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UPC</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__2\">boolean</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mam1665702538335__table_de225b117d4c05a97e99a4c6036b05a1__entry__4\">All uppercase </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Syntax Codes</a><p>Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgx1665702538490.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clearSyntaxProperties()</a><p>Restores the initial values of a field's syntax properties.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dig1665702538574.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getDeclarativeSyntax()</a><p>Return a JavaScript object containing the field syntax properties as defined in the field's definition.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lve1714306731020.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getSyntaxProperty()</a><p>Retrieves the value of the specified syntax property for a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/otb1714306145328.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setSyntaxProperties()</a><p>Sets multiple syntax properties for a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6815675\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6815675\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getSyntaxProperties() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 13, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Retrieves field syntax properties that were set in the browser (using the setSyntaxProperty or setSyntaxProperties functions). Return = FieldObject . getSyntaxProperties () Arguments None Return value Return A a JavaScript object with each attribute representing a syntax field property. For example, in JavaScript Object Notation (JSON), such an object is represented as: Explain this code { \"DIG\" : true, \"LEN\" : { \"min\" : 3, \"max\" : 5 } } Copy Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Description The getSyntaxProperties function only returns properties that were set in the browser using JavaScript, not those that were set in the server before being sent to the browser. The get these properties, use getDeclarativeSyntax . Table 1. Syntax Properties Supported by the JavaScript API Property JavaScript Data Type Values Description/Remarks NED Unsupported. Use property html:readOnly instead — No edit allowed in this field. DIM Unsupported. Use property html:disabled instead — Dim field. No edit and no prompt. REX string Uniface entry format as regex string Regex string for data entry. For example, \"/[a-z]*/i\" (zero or more [a-zA-Z]). For more information, see Field Syntax Codes . ENT string Uniface entry format as syntax string Syntax for data entry. For example, \"&*\" (zero or more [a-zA-Z]). For more information, see Field Syntax Codes . LEN object { min: Number , max: Number } Length of field or subfield. ASC boolean ASCII, in Unicode range 00-7F BRM boolean Check that brackets match. DIG boolean Digits only (0-9) DLS boolean Delete leading spaces. DLZ boolean Delete leading zeros. LOW boolean All lowercase MAN boolean Mandatory field (minimum length of one). NUM boolean Numbers only (0-9, . + -) RCS boolean Replace contiguous spaces with one space. UPC boolean All uppercase Related Links Field Syntax Codes Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only. clearSyntaxProperties() Restores the initial values of a field's syntax properties. getDeclarativeSyntax() Return a JavaScript object containing the field syntax properties as defined in the field's definition. getSyntaxProperty() Retrieves the value of the specified syntax property for a field. setSyntaxProperties() Sets multiple syntax properties for a field. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}